data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
To use, place the window in the lower right part of the screen. Make sure it isn't covering any parts of the fingerprint in GTA. Also make sure you uncheck the "is fullscreen" checkmark if the game is running in windowed mode.
Then, when you're in the GTA hacking menu, press control+s to identify which fingerprints to click. Wait for the program to process, and then choose the images highlighted in green.
Press TAB in GTA to confirm. Then, restart the process. When you're done, press control+x to hide the dialog or press the close button.
